Using the :external+zephyr:ref:`Display driver API <display_api>`
with chosen display. That is:

| :hwftlbl-scr:`LCD` : :dts:`chosen { zephyr,display = &lcd_panel; };`
| :hwftlbl-scr:`ILI9341` : :dts:`lcd_panel: &ili9341_320x240 {};`

